value.0: Benjamin is a man in his early thirties with an easy smile and the steady hands of someone who’s worked honest trade all his life. Having left Baldur’s Gate in search of a quieter, brighter beginning, he’s settled happily in West Southport, where his tidy little grocer’s shop has become a local favorite. He carries himself with a calm, thoughtful air, always ready with a friendly word or a helpful suggestion. There’s a gentleness about him...a sense that he’s grateful for this fresh chapter and eager to share its comforts with anyone who steps inside.
